<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-2">
      <%= render "shared/sidenav" %>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-10">
      <div class="panel panel-primary">
        <div class="panel-heading">
          <h3 class="panel-title">学分提示</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body" style="min-height: 450px">
          <p>满足学习要求是以获取学分是否满足学习要求为判断依据。</p>
          <table class="table table-striped table-bordered table-advance table-hover">
            <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>类别</th>
              <th>公共必修课程及学分</th>
              <th>公共选修课学分要求</th>
              <th>专业核心课学分要求</th>
              <th>总学分要求</th>
            </tr>
            </thead>

            <tbody>
            <tr>
              <th>学习要求</th>
              <td>
                <div>人文系列讲座（1学分)</div>
                <div>中国特色社会主义理论与实践研究（2学分）</div>
                <div>自然辩证法概论（1学分）</div>
                <div>硕士学位英语（英语A）（3学分）</div>
              </td>
              <td>>=2学分</td>
              <td>&gt;=12学分</td>
              <td>&gt;=30学分</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <th>选课情况</th>
              <td>
                <div>人文系列讲座（1学分）</div>
                <div>硕士学位英语（英语A）（3学分）</div>
                <div>中国特色社会主义理论与实践研究（2学分）</div>
              </td>
              <td><%= @credits_public %>学分</td>
              <td><%= @credits_professional %>学分</td>
              <td><%= @credits+6 %>学分</td>
            </tr>
            </tbody>

          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>